room_title: Escape room "Sherlock Holmes and the White Ghost" by AdventurEscape in Hartford
room_address: 1 Corporate Dr, Suite 102 Windsor Locks, CT 06096
room_description: Your detective expertise is needed in a murder mystery case centering around one of Connecticut's most well-documented spirits, the White Lady. The story is inspired by true events, so be careful... Being a skeptic may cost you the case or your life!
